                    "company": "Freelance Actor",
                    "description": "As a freelance actor I worked at company's like\nToneelgroep Amsterdam, Orkater, La Mamma experimental theatre (Italian branche),\nDe Nieuw Amsterdam, Het Geluid Maastricht, Het Huis van Bourgondie, Korzo.\n\nWorked with directors like Gerardjan Rijnders, Paul Knieriem, Lotte de Beer, Niek Kortekaas, Sanne Vogel, Merlijn Twaalfhoven, Isis Freitas Vale Germano\n\nAt festivals like de Parade, Over t IJ, Oerol, Fringes in Amsterdam, Prague, Edinburgh, Grahamstown South africa, and festivals in Bulgaria and Israel and the Palestine territories.\n\nHis solo show LIFE IS TOO GOOD TO BE TRUE won the 2010 Amsterdam Fringe grand prize.\nAnd played more than 50 times around the world. \n\nGable played the leadrole in Theaterfamilie's Junglebook in 2007. Was seen on tv in Stellenbosch, Hotnews.nl and Villa Achterwerk.\n\nHe played a part in the feature film Far from Family.\n\nIn 2014 he will play and sing the part of Tobias in Stephen Sondheim's Sweeney Todd.",
